===The Saxon Stories=== {{main|The Saxon Stories}} Cornwell's latest series focuses on the Anglo-Saxon kingdom of [[Wessex]], England during the 9th-century reign of [[Alfred the Great]], his fierce opposition to the Danes and his determination to unite England as one country. The series, as of 2018, has eleven books.
