'''''Contemporary Wales''''' is published by the [[University of Wales Press]] on behalf of the [[Board of Celtic Studies]].

''Contemporary Wales'' is an annual [[English-language]] journal containing academic articles and reviews relating to [[politics]], [[history]] and current affairs.  It was started in 1987.

It has been digitised by the [[National Library of Wales#Welsh Journals Online|Welsh Journals Online project]] at the [[National Library of Wales]].

