'''Dezső Keresztury''' (6 September 1904 – 30 April 1996) was a [[Hungary|Hungarian]] poet and politician, who served as [[Minister of Education|Minister of Religion and Education]] between 1945 and 1947. He became a member of the [[Hungarian Academy of Sciences]] in 1982.

